-- Calapan Ventures Plans to Build Water System for Philippine City
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-01-03T13:16:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-03/calapan-ventures-plans-to-build-water-system-for-philippine-city.html
Calapan Ventures Inc. (H2O) , a unit of
 Jolliville Holdings Corp. (JOH) , plans to invest about 320 million
pesos ($8 million) to build a water system in La Union, the
utility said in a statement to the Phillipine Stock Exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in London at 
